s="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/four-tet">四岁春节</a>宣布他的全日音乐节将于今年八月重返伦敦芬斯伯里公园。</p><p>制作人本人将在 8 月 10 日星期六举行的活动中演奏长达 5 个小时的节目。名单上还有 Anthony Naples、Champion、DJ ADHD、Mala 等，预计还会有更多人宣布。</p><p>演出门票将于 3 月 5 日上午 11 点开始发售，您可以<a href="https://laylo.com/krankbrother/nW9cq" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。</p><p>伦敦发起人 Krankbrother 在 Instagram 上正式宣布了这项赛事，他写道：“在经历了令人难忘的两年门票售完之后，我们又回来参加第三轮比赛了。在芬斯伯里公园内同一条美丽的绿树成荫的车道上，四岁新年将再次举行比赛不可错过的 5 小时套餐。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3k7IykMFdb/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558